# 4.1.0 (16-04-2015)

	* Remove warning when creating HSSP from sequence (#74)
	* Specify PDB file format requirements in help tour (#70)
	* API example now sends files multipart-encoded (#71)
	* Add feedback(#72), citation(#75), CMBI facilities (#68) links to footer
	* PDB file is now saved when hsspconv fails (#69)
	* Remove vagrant (#67)
	* Add hg-hssp support (#66)

